properties.name: Customer comes with a prescription to pharmacy
Client will enter birth date, contact, info, insurer carrier or confirm the correctness of data
The prescription is automatically sent to the insurence company for check
Technician checks the prescription info correctness
Inform the client that filling the prescription will take time
Perform system check on the prescription
The insurance company checks for correctness
The insurance company check results sent to Pharmacy
Is the medicine needed right away?
Give the medicine and client pays in cash
Put the prescription to the line 1 h before pick-up
Wait for the client to pick up the medicine
The customer hands over his ID
The technician find the correct prescription by the name and legal code
Tell the customer why it was not ready
Give the medicine to the customer and make him pay
